## рҹ”‘ Key Engineering Decisions

### вҡЎ Service Layer Architecture
Keeps controllers thin вҶ’ scalable & testable

### вҡЎ PostgreSQL > MongoDB
Relational data вҶ’ SQL is better choice

### вҡЎ Context API over Redux
Less boilerplate, same control

### вҡЎ JWT Authentication
Stateless вҶ’ better scaling

